Package: InjurySeverityScore
Title: Translate ICD-9 into Injury Severity Score
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Dajun", "Tian", email = "tiandajun@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package InjurySeverityScore calculates the injury severity score (ISS)
    based on the dictionary ICDPIC from ideas.repec.org. The original code was written in 
    Stata, so I implement the same logic in R for easy use.
    Ref: David E. Clark & Turner M. Osler & David R. Hahn, 2009. 
    "ICDPIC: Stata module to provide methods for translating International 
    Classification of Diseases (Ninth Revision) diagnosis codes into standard injury 
    categories and/or scores," Statistical Software Components S457028, 
    Boston College Department of Economics, revised 29 Oct 2010.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.3)
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports: dplyr,
    tidyr
